# Normalize line endings to LF for all text files. Makes Biome format/lint
# deterministic across platforms and resolves the Windows CRLF-checkout false
# failures on `npm run lint` noted in docs/lessons.md (repo blobs are already
# LF; this pins the working tree so tooling agrees everywhere, incl. CI).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never touch line endings.
*.woff2 binary
*.woff binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary

# Text assets that must stay LF.
*.svg text eol=lf
